---
// TheFix.astro
---
<section id="what-makes-us-different" class="relative py-16 px-6 text-base-content border-t border-base-300">
	<div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
		<div class="w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-b from-base-100/0 to-base-200"></div>
	</div>
	<div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto">
		<h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold mb-12 text-center tracking-tight">
			What Makes Our Water Heater Replacement Service Different
		</h2>
		<div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
			<div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg border border-base-300 relative">
				<div class="absolute top-9.5 left-0 w-5 h-5 bg-primary rotate-45 -translate-x-2.5 -translate-y-2.5 rounded-sm rounded-tr-none"></div>
				<div class="card-body">
					<h3 class="card-title text-lg font-semibold">Local, Licensed, and Fully Insured</h3>
					<p class="leading-relaxed">
						We’re not a lead service or franchise—we're based right here in West Michigan. We handle permits, follow code, and carry full insurance so you’re protected at every step.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg border border-base-300 relative">
				<div class="absolute top-9.5 left-0 w-5 h-5 bg-primary rotate-45 -translate-x-2.5 -translate-y-2.5 rounded-sm rounded-tr-none"></div>
				<div class="card-body">
					<h3 class="card-title text-lg font-semibold">Clear, Honest Pricing Up Front</h3>
					<p class="leading-relaxed">
						We provide straightforward quotes with no surprise fees. You'll know exactly what’s included and what your replacement will cost before we begin.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg border border-base-300 relative">
				<div class="absolute top-9.5 left-0 w-5 h-5 bg-primary rotate-45 -translate-x-2.5 -translate-y-2.5 rounded-sm rounded-tr-none"></div>
				<div class="card-body">
					<h3 class="card-title text-lg font-semibold">Fast Turnaround, Same-Day Available</h3>
					<p class="leading-relaxed">
						We’re equipped to handle most replacements the same day you call. No waiting, no wondering when we’ll show up. We respect your time and your comfort.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg border border-base-300 relative">
				<div class="absolute top-9.5 left-0 w-5 h-5 bg-primary rotate-45 -translate-x-2.5 -translate-y-2.5 rounded-sm rounded-tr-none"></div>
				<div class="card-body">
					<h3 class="card-title text-lg font-semibold">Real Experience in the Mechanical Trades</h3>
					<p class="leading-relaxed">
						With 25+ years in HVAC and plumbing systems, we know the details that matter — from code compliance to venting to water line safety. This isn’t a side hustle — it’s our specialty.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg border border-base-300 relative">
				<div class="absolute top-9.5 left-0 w-5 h-5 bg-primary rotate-45 -translate-x-2.5 -translate-y-2.5 rounded-sm rounded-tr-none"></div>
				<div class="card-body">
					<h3 class="card-title text-lg font-semibold">No Sales Gimmicks — Just the Right Fit</h3>
					<p class="leading-relaxed">
						We're not here to upsell you on tankless or the most expensive brand. We install the right size and type for your home, budget, and water usage — and make sure it’s built to last.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg border border-base-300 relative">
				<div class="absolute top-9.5 left-0 w-5 h-5 bg-primary rotate-45 -translate-x-2.5 -translate-y-2.5 rounded-sm rounded-tr-none"></div>
				<div class="card-body">
					<h3 class="card-title text-lg font-semibold">We Respect Your Home</h3>
					<p class="leading-relaxed">
						We get the job done quickly and are mindful you may have other things going on in the home. We clean up thoroughly, and we’re always careful with your property. You can count on us to leave everything better than we found it.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
